Overview
This room takes a deep dive into Meterpreter, the in-memory payload from the Metasploit framework. The focus is on post-exploitation: gathering information, dumping credentials, and pivoting on a compromised Windows host. The challenge at the end simulates an initial SMB compromise and asks you to enumerate the target.

